"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Tracking data shows that at least four ships linked to Iran have crossed the waterway after the US started blocking Iranian ports. China, which buys a lot of Iranian oil, says the US naval blockade is making things worse.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iranian Ships Cross Waterway\",            \"translated_version\": \"Datos muestran que al menos cuatro barcos de Ir\u00e1n cruzaron el agua despu\u00e9s de que EE.UU. empez\u00f3 a bloquear puertos iran\u00edes. China, que compra mucho petr\u00f3leo de Ir\u00e1n, dice que el bloqueo naval de EE.UU. empeora las cosas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Barcos Iran\u00edes Cruzan Agua\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The official tells the BBC that the armed group will not continue talks until Israel fully meets its commitments.\",            \"english_title\": \"Talks on Hold Until Israel Acts\",            \"translated_version\": \"El oficial dice a la BBC que el grupo armado no seguir\u00e1 hablando hasta que Israel cumpla con sus promesas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones en Pausa Hasta que Israel Act\u00fae\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The first trial about Maradona's medical team, who were accused of not taking good care of him, ended because a judge allowed cameras in the court.\",            \"english_title\": \"Maradona's Medical Team Trial Ends\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer juicio sobre el equipo m\u00e9dico de Maradona, acusado de no cuidarlo bien, termin\u00f3 porque un juez permiti\u00f3 c\u00e1maras en la corte.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Juicio del Equipo M\u00e9dico de Maradona Termina\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The son of Marie-Th\u00e9r\u00e8se, who is an elderly woman, is worried about her health while she is held in a Louisiana ICE center.\",            \"english_title\": \"Son Worried About Mother's Health\",            \"translated_version\": \"El hijo de Marie-Th\u00e9r\u00e8se, una mujer mayor, est\u00e1 preocupado por su salud mientras ella est\u00e1 en un centro de ICE en Louisiana.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hijo Preocupado por Salud de Madre\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Students and teachers were among those hurt in an attack in the south-east of the country.\",            \"english_title\": \"Attack Hurts Students and Teachers\",            \"translated_version\": \"Estudiantes y maestros fueron heridos en un ataque en el sureste del pa\u00eds.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque Hiere a Estudiantes y Maestros\"        }    ]}"